<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Dark Pheonix(V3) | Support</title>
    <link
      rel="icon"
      href="https://i.postimg.cc/y87h3x7y/0dc15569002a714e09ef3b03da9ac43d-removebg-preview.png"
      type="image/x-icon"
    />
    <link
      href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@400;600&display=swap"
      rel="stylesheet"
    />
    <style>
      :root {
        --primary: #7289DA;
        --dark: #1e1e2e;
        --darker: #151520;
        --bright: #ffffff;
        --accent: #ff4ecd;
        --discord-bg: #36393f;
        --discord-channel: #2f3136;
      }

      * {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        box-sizing: border-box;
        font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
      }

      body {
        background: var(--darker);
        color: var(--bright);
        min-height: 100vh;
      }

      .navbar {
        background: var(--dark);
        padding: 1rem;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: space-between;
        box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
        flex-wrap: wrap;
      }

      .logo {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 1rem;
      }

      .logo img {
        width: 4rem; /* Slightly larger */
        height: auto;
      }

      .nav-links {
        display: flex;
        gap: 1.5rem;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
      }

      @media (max-width: 768px) {
        .navbar {
          flex-direction: column;
          gap: 1rem;
          text-align: center;
        }

        .nav-links {
          width: 100%;
          justify-content: center;
        }

        .logo {
          width: 100%;
          justify-content: center;
        }
      }

      .nav-links a {
        color: var(--bright);
        text-decoration: none;
        font-weight: 500;
        transition: color 0.3s;
        padding: 0.5rem;
      }

      .nav-links a:hover {
        color: var(--primary);
      }

      main {
        padding: 2rem;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 2rem;
        max-width: 1400px;
        margin: 0 auto;
      }

      h2 {
        font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 3vw, 2rem);
        color: var(--bright);
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
      }

      p,
      ul {
        font-size: clamp(1rem, 2vw, 1.1rem);
        color: #9b9bb1;
      }

      ul {
        list-style: none;
        padding-left: 0;
      }

      li {
        margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
      }

      a {
        color: var(--primary);
        text-decoration: none;
      }

      a:hover {
        text-decoration: underline;
      }

      .card {
        background: var(--dark);
        border-radius: 10px;
        padding: 1.5rem;
        transition: transform 0.3s;
        border: 1px solid transparent;
      }

      .card:hover {
        transform: translateY(-5px);
        border-color: var(--primary);
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="glow"></div>

    <nav class="navbar">
      <div class="logo">
        <img
          src="https://i.postimg.cc/y87h3x7y/0dc15569002a714e09ef3b03da9ac43d-removebg-preview.png"
          alt="Dark Phoenix Logo"
        />
        <h1>Dark Phoenix (V3)</h1>
      </div>
      <div class="nav-links">
        <a href="/">Home</a>
        <a href="/commands">Commands</a>
        <a href="/user-settings">Settings</a>
        <a href="/support">Support</a>
        <a href="/forum">Forum</a>
      </div>
    </nav>

  <main>
    <div class="card">
      <h2>Support</h2>
      <p>If you need help, feel free to reach out to our support team. We're here to assist you with any issues or questions.</p>
      <p>Contact us through the following channels:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Email: <a href="mailto:mark.lane001@icloud.com">support@dark-pheonix.com</a></li>
        <li>Discord: <a href="https://discord.gg/FnGse6AvNR">Join our Discord server</a></li>
        <li>Forum: <a href="/forum">Visit our support forum</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </main>
</body>
</html>
